    "comment": "Rationale: Fig1A: Immunocytochemistry shows that immunoreaction product of endogenous APPL1 colocalises with postsynaptic marker PSD95 (marked by white arrows). Almost 90% of the PSD95 clusters colocalize with APPL1 in excitatory hippocampal neurons.\n\n\"Postsynapse\" was chosen as the SynGO term, instead of a more specific term due to the lack of relevant evidence.. Experimental description: Low density hippocampal neuronal cultures were prepared and maintained as previously described (Goslin et al., 1998).",
